649", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "b93a4da75bb23a53b0666250d836f4df55cab3816189050a605898d88bd9b2b6", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "eb1dbb22-0a57-4838-8640-5328ca0926c4", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "bd7bab1766ec66191cd9d2aeda6ed892eceb1c749dc63b250bcd74ff0ca7d611", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Copyright \u00a9 2015 Acumen Business Systems Ltd www.acumensystems.com\nPage 1 of 5\n\n2. USE OF CONFIDENTIAL INFORMATION\n\n2.1. A Receiving Party agrees:\n\n2.1.1.\n\n1. to keep the Confidential Information of the other strictly confidential and not copy, supply or make the same available to any person other than as permitted in Clauses 2.1.2 and 2.1.3 below;", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1314, "end_char_idx": 1664, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "eb1dbb22-0a57-4838-8640-5328ca0926c4": {"__data__": {"id_": "eb1dbb22-0a57-4838-8640-5328ca0926c4", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "a515967c-bf96-4238-8aa0-bd728cb0b0a6", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "93db7d117b44f544615900f208a07ba9ee57530b6f3b2b0cccfdc80b7250161e", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "368fb8fa-a812-4d73-a875-5f47671c571b", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "f935bbadf43e2fc0c0101dee769e20ac3336ae2bb5b7316f194e504b0e1bf8f8", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "028ef285-f335-40cf-b3bf-8f9b660a4697", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "967401e34d2e8100deea3de43c6dc0f29c5998104f2afbb009cb3bce728d1a4f", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "2.1.2. to use the Confidential Information of the other solely in,\n\n and to the extent necessary for the Purpose and not to copy or use any Confidential Information of the other save to the extent necessary for the Purpose;\n\n2.1.3.\n\n not to disclose any Confidential Information to any person or entity other than to such of its employees who need to know for the Purpose (\u201cPermitted Disclosees\u201d),", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1666, "end_char_idx": 2063, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "028ef285-f335-40cf-b3bf-8f9b660a4697": {"__data__": {"id_": "028ef285-f335-40cf-b3bf-8f9b660a4697", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "a515967c-bf96-4238-8aa0-bd728cb0b0a6", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "93db7d117b44f544615900f208a07ba9ee57530b6f3b2b0cccfdc80b7250161e", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "eb1dbb22-0a57-4838-8640-5328ca0926c4", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "bd7bab1766ec66191cd9d2aeda6ed892eceb1c749dc63b250bcd74ff0ca7d611", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "2de3ba60-edd5-4d57-bf06-2a18c21366f8", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "91a3bc33bcf0859818398b88ce3043da3e6083a7fc9e0ca966576e9d1a2c6ebc", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "provided that the Receiving Party shall ensure that its Permitted Disclosees keep all Confidential Information confidential and only use it on the terms of this Agreement, as if such Permitted Disclosees were party to this Agreement.\n\n3. CARE\n\n3.1. Without prejudice to the generality of Clause 2,\n\n the Receiving Party shall exercise no less a degree of care in protecting the Confidential Information than which it uses to protect its own information of like sensitivity and importance.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2064, "end_char_idx": 2552, "metadata_seperator": "\n"